  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 5)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package operates at Model Risk Level 5 due to elevated patient risk and high model influence. Several credibility factors remain not-assessed without documented justification, materially weakening the overall credibility argument.",
